∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] {γ : ℂ → E}, 
  (∀ z, DifferentiableAt ℂ γ z) → (∮ (z : ℂ) in γ, 0) = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] {f : ℂ → E} {γ : Path ℂ},
  (∀ z, DifferentiableAt ℂ f z) → γ.IsLoop → (∮ z in γ, f z) = 0

∀ {U : Type u_1} [inst : TopologicalSpace U] [inst_1 : ComplexManifold U] {γ : Path ℂ} {f : ℂ → ℂ},
  HolomorphicOn f U → γ.IsLoop → ShIntegral f γ = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] {f : ℂ → E} {γ : Path ℂ},
  (∀ z, DifferentiableAt ℂ f z) → γ.isClosed → (∮ (z : ℂ) in γ, f z) = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] {f : ℂ → E} {γ : ℂ → ℂ} [inst_2 : IsClosed γ],
  (∀ z, DifferentiableAt ℂ f z) → ShIntegral γ f = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] {f : ℂ → E} {γ : Path ℂ},
  (∀ z ∈ Set.Univ, DifferentiableAt ℂ f z) → (∮ (z : ℂ) in γ, f z) = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] {γ : Path ℂ},
  IsClosed γ → (∮ (z : ℂ) in γ, f z) = 0

∀ {E : Type u} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] {f : ℂ → E} {γ : ℂ → ℂ},
  HolomorphicAt ℂ f (γ 0) → (∮ z in MeasureTheory.Measure.map γ MeasureTheory.Measure.zero, f z) = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] {f : ℂ → E} {γ : Path ℂ},
  (∀ z ∈ γ.range, DifferentiableAt ℂ f z) → ShIntegral ℂ γ f = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] {γ : ℂ → ℂ} {f : ℂ → E},
  (∀ z, DifferentiableAt ℂ f z) → (∮ z in γ, f z) = 0
